org.dgfoundation.amp.newreports

Class HeaderCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.ReportHeadingCell
      • org.dgfoundation.amp.newreports.HeaderCell

  • public class HeaderCell
extends ReportHeadingCell
    Pre-generated Report Header Cell per tabular view, that provides its positioning information, reusing ReportHeadingCell. It can be used to facilitate different clients from repeatedly building their own headers structure.
